reviewText: All I have to say is that many years ago their was a man named Thomas..."A doubting Thomas" and he doubted the most important event in history ! Although the information on this video is not as important as the evidence and Truth that Thomas finally came to except when shown in front of his own eyes  ,this RODS video  may give some of us the mind set that Thomas once had until we see the evidence and truth for ourselves right in front of our own eyes. This is a very interesting video ! and these things called RODS may be real. I will be watching the skies much closer now after watching this video.
